3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a compensation framework which dynamically chooses the most appropriate face recognition system. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with identity inference. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with surveillance environments and face recognition systems which have security implications.
